title: S16 Ep89: Witchcraft, Magic and the Art of Necromancy w/ Dan & Kat Eckhart
itunes:title: Witchcraft, Magic and the Art of Necromancy w/ Dan & Kat Eckhart
description:
Darkness Radio presents Witchcraft, Magic and the Art of Necromancy with Dan & Kat Eckhart

Dave Schrader from the #HolzerFiles & Darkness Radio is joined my mystic art practitioners Dan & Kat Eckhart to discuss a myriad of fascinating topics, from tapping into magic, the mystery of witchcraft and speaking with and dealing with the dead!

PLUS we will take YOUR questions and thoughts!

Visit the Eckhart's here: www.theeckharts.com

Come see Dave this month at Michigan ParaCon: www.MIParacon.com
